title: PS3 Ion Assault [PSN]
description:
In ISO format.




    Summary: Ion Assault HD is an arcade-style action game in which players control a small space ship that blasts asteroids and battles enemy ships.



    Official PlayStation Magazine Benelux


    We're no diehard fans of the genre, but we can certainly appreciate a good shmup from time to time. Especially if the visuals are as impressive as those of Ion Assault. The basic idea is that you suck up ions and use them as ammunition against the enemy.
